#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.76:0.2"
msgid "8. Ākaṅkhavagga "
msgstr "8. If You Want "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.76:0.3"
msgid "76. Tayodhammasutta "
msgstr "76. Three Things "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an10.76:1.1"
msgid "“Tayome, bhikkhave, dhammā loke na saṃvijjeyyuṃ, na tathāgato loke uppajjeyya arahaṃ sammāsambuddho, na tathāgatappavedito dhammavinayo loke dibbeyya. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, if three things were not found, the Realized One, the perfected one, the fully awakened Buddha would not arise in the world, and the teaching and training proclaimed by the Realized One would not shine in the world. "

msgctxt "an10.76:1.2"
msgid "Katame tayo? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "an10.76:1.3"
msgid "Jāti ca, jarā ca, maraṇañca—"
msgstr "Rebirth, old age, and death. "

msgctxt "an10.76:1.4"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo dhammā loke na saṃvijjeyyuṃ, na tathāgato loke uppajjeyya arahaṃ sammāsambuddho, na tathāgatappavedito dhammavinayo loke dibbeyya. "
msgstr "If these three things were not found, the Realized One, the perfected one, the fully awakened Buddha would not arise in the world, and the teaching and training proclaimed by the Realized One would not shine in the world. "

msgctxt "an10.76:1.5"
msgid "Yasmā ca kho, bhikkhave, ime tayo dhammā loke saṃvijjanti tasmā tathāgato loke uppajjati arahaṃ sammāsambuddho, tasmā tathāgatappavedito dhammavinayo loke dibbati. "
msgstr "But since these three things are found, the Realized One, the perfected one, the fully awakened Buddha arises in the world, and the teaching and training proclaimed by the Realized One shines in the world. "

