msgctxt "an10.76:20.3"
msgid "Ahirikaṃ pahāya, anottappaṃ pahāya, pamādaṃ pahāya—"
msgstr "Lack of conscience, imprudence, and negligence. "

msgctxt "an10.76:20.4"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo dhamme pahāya bhabbo anādariyaṃ pahātuṃ dovacassataṃ pahātuṃ pāpamittataṃ pahātuṃ. (9) "
msgstr "After giving up these three things you can give up disregard, being hard to admonish, and having bad friends. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.149, sc21
msgctxt "an10.76:21.1"
msgid "Hirīmāyaṃ, bhikkhave, ottāpī appamatto hoti. "
msgstr "Mendicants, someone who has conscience and prudence is diligent. "

msgctxt "an10.76:21.2"
msgid "So appamatto samāno bhabbo anādariyaṃ pahātuṃ dovacassataṃ pahātuṃ pāpamittataṃ pahātuṃ. "
msgstr "When you’re diligent you can give up disregard, being hard to admonish, and having bad friends. "

msgctxt "an10.76:21.3"
msgid "So kalyāṇamitto samāno bhabbo assaddhiyaṃ pahātuṃ avadaññutaṃ pahātuṃ kosajjaṃ pahātuṃ. "
msgstr "When you’ve got good friends you can give up faithlessness, uncharitableness, and laziness. "

msgctxt "an10.76:21.4"
msgid "So āraddhavīriyo samāno bhabbo uddhaccaṃ pahātuṃ asaṃvaraṃ pahātuṃ dussilyaṃ pahātuṃ. "
msgstr "When you’re energetic you can give up restlessness, lack of restraint, and unethical conduct. "

msgctxt "an10.76:21.5"
msgid "So sīlavā samāno bhabbo ariyānaṃ adassanakamyataṃ pahātuṃ ariyadhammassa asotukamyataṃ pahātuṃ upārambhacittataṃ pahātuṃ. "
msgstr "When you’re ethical you can give up not wanting to see the noble ones, not wanting to hear the teaching of the noble ones, and a fault-finding mind. "

msgctxt "an10.76:21.6"
msgid "So anupārambhacitto samāno bhabbo muṭṭhassaccaṃ pahātuṃ asampajaññaṃ pahātuṃ cetaso vikkhepaṃ pahātuṃ. "
msgstr "When you don’t have a fault-finding mind you can give up unmindfulness, lack of situational awareness, and a distracted mind. "

msgctxt "an10.76:21.7"
msgid "So avikkhittacitto samāno bhabbo ayonisomanasikāraṃ pahātuṃ kummaggasevanaṃ pahātuṃ cetaso līnattaṃ pahātuṃ. "
msgstr "When your mind isn’t scattered you can give up improper attention, following a wrong path, and mental sluggishness. "

msgctxt "an10.76:21.8"
msgid "So alīnacitto samāno bhabbo sakkāyadiṭṭhiṃ pahātuṃ vicikicchaṃ pahātuṃ sīlabbataparāmāsaṃ pahātuṃ. "
msgstr "When your mind isn’t sluggish you can give up identity view, doubt, and misapprehension of precepts and observances. "

msgctxt "an10.76:21.9"
msgid "So avicikiccho samāno bhabbo rāgaṃ pahātuṃ dosaṃ pahātuṃ mohaṃ pahātuṃ. "
msgstr "When you have no doubts you can give up greed, hate, and delusion. "

msgctxt "an10.76:21.10"
msgid "So rāgaṃ pahāya dosaṃ pahāya mohaṃ pahāya bhabbo jātiṃ pahātuṃ jaraṃ pahātuṃ maraṇaṃ pahātun”ti. (10) "
msgstr "After giving up greed, hate, and delusion you can give up rebirth, old age, and death.” "

